snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS HD 1.5 + 2.5 ReMIX – Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Celebrate 15 years of KINGDOM HEARTS with this essential HD collection featuring six unforgettable KINGDOM HEARTS adventures:
 
• KINGDOM HEARTS FINAL MIX
• KINGDOM HEARTS Re:Chain of Memories
• KINGDOM HEARTS 358/2 Days (HD remastered cinematics)
• KINGDOM HEARTS II FINAL MIX
• KINGDOM HEARTS Birth by Sleep FINAL MIX
• KINGDOM HEARTS Re:coded

Coming to PlayStation 4 on March 28, 2017 in North America, 31 March 2017 in Europe.

Pre-Order: http://bit.ly/2eJYZsk
